  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the chicken pieces onto skewers.",
    "In a bowl, whisk together yoghurt, lime juice, garlic, ginger, salt, and pepper.",
    "Brush the yoghurt mixture onto the chicken skewers.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Serve the chicken skewers in agave leaves.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy.",
